pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mur1719469754461.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mur1719469754461.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mur1719469754461.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aep1665703127391\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      List\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"aep1665703127391__list_387083\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Displays the field as a list box showing the possible values, of which one or more can be selected.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"aep1665703127391__topic_d115232e1_d115233e1_d115234e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6260e17\">XHTML Specification: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"select\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6260e23\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fdp1719467376341.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" title=\"XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.\">&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665703127391__topic_d81777e1_d81778e1_d81779e1_d81780e1_d81781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d753296e72\">\n                       \n Widget Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oco1665703109723.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oco1665703109723.html\" title=\"This property defines ValRep list for the static server page widget.\">Value/Representation</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__2\">Specify the values and their representations of\n                        the items in the widget.<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e54\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The format of the values in the\n                           ValRep must be same as the display format of the field.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pne1665703108090.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pne1665703108090.html\" title=\"In a static server page, exclude the field or entity if it does not need to be sent to the browser.\">Exclude</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aep1665703127391__d6261e20__entry__2\">Do not load the field in the server page\n\t\t\t\t if it does not need to be sent to the browser. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665703127391__topic_d81787e1_d81788e1_d81789e1_d81790e1_d81791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d753296e141\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__p_d115253e1_d115254e1_d115255e1\">When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following, in which each <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Value/Representation</span> pair is defined as an option:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-subst size=\"10\" name=\"LIST.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"select\"&gt;\n &lt;select name=\"LIST.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" size=\"4\"&gt;\n &lt;option&gt;List&lt;/option&gt;\n &lt;/select&gt;\n&lt;/x-subst&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__p_d115256e1_d115257e1_d115258e1\">The list and menu USP widgets differ in that the size of the list control is greater than 1 and the size of the menu control is equal to 1.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aep1665703127391__topic_d81792e1_d81793e1_d81794e1_d81795e1_d81796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d753296e159\">\n                       ValRep Handling</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__p_d115262e1_d115263e1_d115264e1\">The widget uses the ValRep list defined for the field to build up the options visible in the list. It expects a list of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>=<var class=\"keyword varname\">Representation</var> pairs and displays the representations in the list. If a ValRep item does not have a <var class=\"keyword varname\">Representation</var>, the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> is displayed instead. When the user selects an item in the list, the corresponding value is selected.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__p_d115265e1_d115266e1_d115267e1\">If you want to define an empty string value as one of the items in the list,\n\t\t enter a representation without a corresponding value. You can test for empty string values by\n\t\t testing for an empty string (\"\").</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aep1665703127391__p_d115268e1_d115269e1_d115270e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hdy1665702557196.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdy1665702557196.html\" title=\"This property defines the possible values that the field accepts. The ValRep consists of a Uniface list of one or more items, in which each item consists of a value and optional representation.\">ValRep</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bfp1719419687677.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu</a><p>This widget displays the field as a list box of possible values, of which one or more can be selected.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422343\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "List Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 List Displays the field as a list box showing the possible values, of which one or more can be selected. XHTML Specification: <x-subst type=\"select\"> For more information, see <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> . Widget Properties Table 1. Widget Properties Property Description Value/Representation Specify the values and their representations of the items in the widget. Note: The format of the values in the ValRep must be same as the display format of the field. Exclude Do not load the field in the server page if it does not need to be sent to the browser. Description When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following, in which each Value/Representation pair is defined as an option: <x-subst size=\"10\" name=\"LIST.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"select\"> <select name=\"LIST.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" size=\"4\"> <option>List</option> </select> </x-subst> Copy The list and menu USP widgets differ in that the size of the list control is greater than 1 and the size of the menu control is equal to 1. ValRep Handling The widget uses the ValRep list defined for the field to build up the options visible in the list. It expects a list of Value = Representation pairs and displays the representations in the list. If a ValRep item does not have a Representation , the Value is displayed instead. When the user selects an item in the list, the corresponding value is selected. If you want to define an empty string value as one of the items in the list, enter a representation without a corresponding value. You can test for empty string values by testing for an empty string (\"\"). For more information, see ValRep . Related Links Menu This widget displays the field as a list box of possible values, of which one or more can be selected. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}